children.text: In this event I have annotated a performance done by Maya Angelou performing her seminal poem "And Still I Rise". This piece is a great canidate for annotation as the performance has many shifts in tempo, pitch, and, volume.

citation: Angelou, Maya. And Still I Rise, ia800109.us.archive.org/15/items/Podcast31018/Podcast%203-10-18.mp3. Accessed 28 Mar. 2025.
